How hypoxia regulate exosomes in ischemic diseases and cancer microenvironment?

Yaghoubi S(1), Najminejad H(2), Dabaghian M(3), Karimi MH(4), 
Abdollahpour-Alitappeh M(5), Rad F(6)(7), Mahi-Birjand M(8), Mohammadi S(9), 
