Cost-Effectiveness Analysis of Screening for Persistent Hepatitis E Virus 
Infection in Solid Organ Transplant Patients in the United Kingdom: A 
Model-Based Economic Evaluation.

Ankcorn MJ(1), Tedder RS(2), Cairns J(3), Sandmann FG(4).

